This is a medium/large sized Fight Yard style map inspired by the game A3P. Enjoy!

Please leave a comment and rate, thank you!

-	64 Spawns
-	Nav file for bots
-	Overview Radar Map
-	Cube Maps
-	3d Skybox
-	Optimized for better FPS
-	Everything is packaged into the .bsp with Pakrat
-	Custom Textures from [-B-]
-	Custom Textures from Eric

Please leave a comment and rate, thank you!
